{"tid":2395866,"cid":4,"subCid":0,"title":"雙 8K 顯示　Apple 頭戴式 Mixed-Reality 裝置定價或高達 3000 美元","createTime":"2021-02-05T07:22:27.000Z","updateTime":"2021-02-14T13:07:53.000Z","uid":10788,"like":2,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":25,"replies":[{"pid":"c33561a9c3c908f0a4de4f8a0668104549b35e20","tid":2395866,"uid":10788,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-05T07:22:27.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.newmobilelife.com/2021/02/05/apple-mixed-reality/?utm_source=rss&amp;utm_medium=rss&amp;utm_campaign=apple-mixed-reality\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.newmobilelife.com%2F2021%2F02%2F05%2Fapple-mixed-reality%2F%3Futm_source%3Drss%26utm_medium%3Drss%26utm_campaign%3Dapple-mixed-reality&d=GtJgxCFvwMhqeg%2B2Fxb9Eb1zpTq0bGO0w7tnLPpoXkc%3D&h=2baed9e1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.newmobilelife.com/2021/02/05/apple-mixed-reality/?utm_source=rss&amp;utm_medium=rss&amp;utm_campaign=apple-mixed-reality</a><br />\n<br />\n早前有消息指 Apple 會推出 VR／AR 裝置，但定價相當高，預計 Apple Store 每天也只是能賣出一套。而 The Information 引述知情人指 Apple 正開發一種 Mixed-Reality（混合真實）頭戴式裝置，它會配上超過 12 個鏡頭，用作追蹤手部動作及顯示周圍的環境。而顯示方面會有兩面 8K 螢幕，因此成本也會很高。另外，Apple 會有高階的眼球追蹤技術，例如只刷新改變了的區域部份，從而加快螢幕顯示反應。<br />\n<br />\n而售價方面，成本相信會較 Facebook 的 Oculus 高 300 美元至 1000 美元，因此 Apple 內部評估定價可能高達 3000 美元。事實上，Microsoft 的 HoloLens 定價也是在 3500 美元水平，因此估計這款產品會針對商用市場。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://chinese.engadget.com/apple-mixed-reality-headset-price-specs-rumor-043345734.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fchinese.engadget.com%2Fapple-mixed-reality-headset-price-specs-rumor-043345734.html&d=GtJgxCFvwMhqeg%2B2Fxb9Eb1zpTq0bGO0w7tnLPpoXkc%3D&h=785f4711\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://chinese.engadget.com/apple-mixed-reality-headset-price-specs-rumor-043345734.html</a><br />\n<br />\nApple 籌備已久的 VR/AR 裝置，日前又有了新的消息被曝光出來。據 The Information 從「內部知情人士」處聽來的說法，這款混合實境裝置在樣式上似乎跟傳統 VR 產品相近，其頭帶可以更換，而且也將搭載專用的自研晶片和「空間音訊」功能所需用到的組件。據說它將配備兩片 8K 螢幕，同時有超過 12 顆相機用於追蹤動作和外部環境。此外近年在 Apple 新品中越來越常見的 LiDAR 技術也會採用，可以幫助裝置更好地測量現實世界中的距離和範圍。<br />\n<br />\n報導中提到相關的開發其實已經到了比較靠後的階段，如果一切順利的話產品最早在 2022 年便會問世，而其售價或許會來到 US$3,000（約 HK$23,260 / NT$83,940）。如果情況的確如此的話，從目前看到的硬體配置來說，這定價倒也並非不合理。只是這樣一來產品的定位，可能相對來說會更遠離大眾市場，而是更靠近微軟 HoloLens 2 所在的企業領域。"},{"pid":"7087837cf66fd3bbacbbafcf264a39a6764e852b","tid":2395866,"uid":2403,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-05T07:28:04.000Z","msg":"LM"},{"pid":"b2b93286423482a7f050dba977341e4abce0dbee","tid":2395866,"uid":66365,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-05T07:44:25.000Z","msg":"有撚卡頂到8K 咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a86afca581733787e4961428ffaca70ffe11a348","tid":2395866,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":13,"score":-13,"quote":{"pid":"b2b93286423482a7f050dba977341e4abce0dbee","tid":2395866,"uid":66365,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-05T07:44:25.000Z","msg":"有撚卡頂到8K 咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":5,"replyTime":"2021-02-05T08:01:50.000Z","msg":"雙卡gtx3060 ti"},{"pid":"029139232c974ea058541f63ea3552df2084cb34","tid":2395866,"uid":27432,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-05T08:08:38.000Z","msg":"APPLE 點會出呢D 野<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8d3281f3df8e703f467e0bb7a798a5283fdedb04","tid":2395866,"uid":14494,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"a86afca581733787e4961428ffaca70ffe11a348","tid":2395866,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":13,"score":-13,"quote":{"pid":"b2b93286423482a7f050dba977341e4abce0dbee","tid":2395866,"uid":66365,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-05T07:44:25.000Z","msg":"有撚卡頂到8K 咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":5,"replyTime":"2021-02-05T08:01:50.000Z","msg":"雙卡gtx3060 ti"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-05T08:09:35.000Z","msg":"戴係個頭度？"},{"pid":"c569a2a9fd680e6070f458c92ea40cf2